attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: Historic charm meets modern city living in the heart of Fort Point. This brick-and-beam loft puts you in the center of it all—waterfront strolls, coffee at Flour, and dinner at Boston’s top restaurants. With 13’ ceilings and oversized south-facing windows, natural light floods the space, perfect for both work and entertaining. The 2BR/1BA layout is designed for flexibility, featuring a sleek kitchen with Bosch appliances and Zebrawood cabinetry. The second bedroom adapts to your needs—guest room, office, or creative space—while custom walnut built-ins, a Murphy bed, and extra storage maximize every inch. Enjoy the ease of a professionally managed building with a lobby lounge, elevator, bike storage, and a rooftop deck with skyline views. The Harborwalk, Trader Joe’s, and boutique fitness studios are moments away, with Seaport’s best dining and nightlife at your fingertips.
